nietzsche destroys christian dogma with this book nietzsche is a genius . his ideas are still as important today as they were the day he wrote them . he destroys christianity in one fell swoop - anyone who reads the will to power and still believes in christian dogma is in the purest state of denial . nietzsche provides saying after saying after saying , perfect for debate . if you 're a doubter or secular , read this book and you will erase all possibilities of the bible being real from your mind forever